commit.message: Updated ruff config, fixed several legacy code issues
Modernized code: f-strings, improved typing information
Switched from flake8 to ruff as linter
Nox: Added option to run individual tests, usage of more f-strings
Better source distribution: Include docs and test suite
Add flit to required libs for building the distribution files
A more recent version of helpers using f-strings (with respect to Py3)
Removed Python 2 statement from docs. Py2 isn't tested anymore
